{"id":"entities/africa","title":"Africa","type":"entities","html":"<h1>Africa</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. Africa over-indexes in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-05-20-side-quests-list\">the May 20 side quests list</a> — appears twice (\"ride train across africa\" + \"live amongst african villages\") out of five total bullets. The deepest unscratched travel itch in the post-<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/china-chapter\">China chapter</a> period.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Open questions</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Which train? (Tazara, Cape-to-Cairo, other?)</li>\n<li>Which countries / villages? Yahir doesn't specify.</li>\n<li>Does Africa ever resurface in 2026 notes, or did the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/austin-tx\">Austin</a> / <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/rankett\">Rankett</a> focus pull it off the radar?</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Related</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-05-20-side-quests-list\">2025 05 20 side quests list</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/china-chapter\">china chapter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/non-negotiables-for-traveling\">non negotiables for traveling</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/six-month-adventure-creed\">six month adventure creed</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/austin-tx\">austin tx</a></li>\n</ul>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/austin-tx","label":"Austin, Texas"},{"id":"entities/block-inc","label":"Block Inc."},{"id":"concepts/china-chapter","label":"China Chapter"},{"id":"summaries/2023-01-30-eli-internship","label":"ELI Internship Application"},{"id":"concepts/non-negotiables-for-traveling","label":"Non-Negotiables for Traveling"},{"id":"summaries/2021-04-28-proscons-travel-vs-work","label":"Pros & Cons — Travel vs Work (Summer 2021)